Name: VERIFY COUCH CONFIGURATION
checklistText:
VERIFY COUCH CONFIGURATION

	MDC assist bar – extd & locked
	Headrests – soft suit position
	THC armrest in launch position & locked
	Indb arm rests – stowed & contr locked
	Couches – launch/entry position (Y-Y
		struts extd & locked)
	Seat pans - 85° position & locked
O2/comm umb – stowed
Harnesses & restraints – extd & laid aside
Couch stab brace – stowed
Egress CM

Steps.Text: Toggle seats to normal launch config (visible)
